Patch Set 1:

While I am a fan of GPFS, and I have been delinquent on helping with the following issue,  I think we should be careful about accepting too many storage drivers into the codebase.  Active support may come and go.  Some set of storage drivers should be a part of core set but we should carefully evaluate that set.
